| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2576 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 49f89c26-b70f-548a-9a24-509574ef9e53"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
